  "detailed_description": "<h1>More from Nibb Games</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745800/extras/64a04ea0580bd959b5d23684ebf8fa00.avif?t=1718924365\" width=622 height=188 /></span><br><br><strong>Some greedy businessmen decided to destroy the forest, to create the construction of a giant building. And with this several animals were expelled from their homes, seeing this, their role will be to prevent this construction from continuing, eliminating all the robots in the area and thus managing to save the forest.</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>50 stages with more than 8 mechanics!</strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745800/extras/f0f75fa2b43dfe91132c84c41506a027.poster.avif?t=1718924365\" width=622 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745800/extras/f0f75fa2b43dfe91132c84c41506a027.webm?t=1718924365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745800/extras/f0f75fa2b43dfe91132c84c41506a027.mp4?t=1718924365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Different ways to beat each stage!</strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745800/extras/f79d9b81601d0482d7f30f29e34239a4.poster.avif?t=1718924365\" width=622 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745800/extras/f79d9b81601d0482d7f30f29e34239a4.webm?t=1718924365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745800/extras/f79d9b81601d0482d7f30f29e34239a4.mp4?t=1718924365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Different ways to eliminate each enemy!</strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745800/extras/1317362ae48142dbd2ad506862d48cf6.poster.avif?t=1718924365\" width=622 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745800/extras/1317362ae48142dbd2ad506862d48cf6.webm?t=1718924365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745800/extras/1317362ae48142dbd2ad506862d48cf6.mp4?t=1718924365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
